<p><b>William Olaf Stapledon</b> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1886-05-10"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="05-10"><a href="/wiki/May_10" title="May 10">May 10</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1886" title="1886">1886</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1950-09-06"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="09-06"><a href="/wiki/September_6" title="September 6">September 6</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1950" title="1950">1950</a></span>) was a <a href="/wiki/United_Kingdom" title="United Kingdom">British</a> philosopher and author of several influential works of <a href="/wiki/Science_fiction" title="Science fiction">science fiction</a>.</p>
